tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE RiskMetrics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  stock_symbol VARCHAR(255),
  trading_strategy VARCHAR(255),
  trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  buy_quantity INT,
  sell_quantity INT,
  risk_score DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE RiskMetrics (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	symbol TEXT,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP,
	alpha FLOAT,
	beta FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE TradingAlgorithms (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	name TEXT,
	description TEXT,
	strategy TEXT,
	parameters JSON
);

CREATE TABLE TradeOrders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(50),
  order_type VARCHAR(10),
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL(10,2),
  order_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE trade_executions (
	execution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	strategy_id INT,
	symbol VARCHAR(255),
	executed_price DECIMAL(10,2),
	quantity INT,
	execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trade_logs (
	log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	execution_id INT,
	symbol VARCHAR(255),
	log_message TEXT,
	log_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TradeExecution (
   trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   instrument_id INT,
   algorithm_id INT,
   execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
   volume INT,
   price FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE HistoricalData (
   data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   instrument_id INT,
   timestamp TIMESTAMP,
   price FLOAT,
   volume_traded INT
);
